            "body": "Backport failed for `release-0.12`, because it was unable to cherry-pick the commit(s).\n\nPlease cherry-pick the changes locally and resolve any conflicts.\n```bash\ngit fetch origin release-0.12\ngit worktree add -d .worktree/backport-39525-to-release-0.12 origin/release-0.12\ncd .worktree/backport-39525-to-release-0.12\ngit switch --create backport-39525-to-release-0.12\ngit cherry-pick -x b56f7c6edd339ab8be32738f1ecb0d7056b7ab9c\n```",
